{"tid":1598990,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭宣佈香港自治並非一國兩制","createTime":"2019-09-27T17:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:37:42.000Z","uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"245afb11b6bd2ee0d7f0a9a5eee17f4f8795217a","tid":1598990,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"［文長］希望睇曬佢<br />\n我都知好多人唔鐘意神駒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申唔係fans<br />\n但係作為深黃既香港人<br />\n更加應該睇下唔同政見 藍屍 黃絲既睇法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">保持獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pXi48TM2TCI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpXi48TM2TCI&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=d7873914\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pXi48TM2TCI</a><br />\n佢有幾個point個人覺得分析得唔錯<br />\n2:52 高度自治非自治<br />\n有句comment個人覺得好啱<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高度自治=高度(相似)自治既假自治</span></span><br />\n大家自行分析 我都咀嚼左好耐呢一段既說話<br />\n<br />\n之後就係講成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五大訴求裡第二較易得手就係呢個<br />\n成立左 popo必成condom <br />\n但係調查時限係幾耐？邊個查 邊度開始落手查<br />\n呢個仆街政府咁叻拖同玩言語藝術<br />\n假如成功爭取<br />\n請各位真&middot;香港人發揮我地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">投訴精神</span></span>唔好就咁算<br />\n講咁撚多結論就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要雙普選</span><br />\n<br />\n心水清既人都知 人數少左好多<br />\n運動去到一個平台期<br />\n膠post都上到熱門 po story怒屌既港女都變返飲飲食食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要爭取到底 <br />\n一定要有雙普選先收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醒啦喂 好多行動post推唔郁上熱門</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 <br />\n缺一不可<br />\n勿忘721 811 831 同所有義士<br />\n生之為人 不忍沉默<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"979f853862290452cce1fb4eea832b5ae99748e4","tid":1598990,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"358dab6a683d5311784cb48558dc357995e78815","tid":1598990,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yMnCTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yMnCTO.jpg&h=24873515&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7fc07f6ec7a179e0a69f5a0c46f7db5f4cc9949","tid":1598990,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"我要雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5f2e5048a9b641f83daa709fc07547352452f7","tid":1598990,"uid":112691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}